      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "祢衡更衣，上。",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02003021_e00002",
      "play_id": "02003021",
      "scene_id": "02003021_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 2,
      "seq_in_scene": 2,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "唱",
      "speakers": [
        "祢衡"
      ],
      "text": "丞相宽限岂宁坐，披星戴月渡江河。招安降事若不妥，死在他乡做鬼魔。",
      "text_length": 32
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02003021_e00003",
      "play_id": "02003021",
      "scene_id": "02003021_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 3,
      "seq_in_scene": 3,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "祢衡下。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02003021_e00004",
      "play_id": "02003021",
      "scene_id": "02003021_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 4,
      "seq_in_scene": 4,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "唱",
      "speakers": [
        "曹操"
      ],
      "text": "祢衡说话真可恶，舌尖犹如刺人戈。",
      "text_length": 16
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02003021_e00005",
      "play_id": "02003021",
      "scene_id": "02003021_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 5,
      "seq_in_scene": 5,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "同白",
      "speakers": [
        "众人"
      ],
      "text": "丞相，祢衡放肆，反命荆州为吏何故？",
      "text_length": 17
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02003021_e00006",
      "play_id": "02003021",
      "scene_id": "02003021_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 6,
      "seq_in_scene": 6,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "曹操"
      ],
      "text": "若将他斩首，天下人道老夫不能容物。命他荆州为吏，借刘表杀之，岂不为美哉？",
      "text_length": 36
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02003021_e00007",
      "play_id": "02003021",
      "scene_id": "02003021_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 7,
      "seq_in_scene": 7,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "同白",
      "speakers": [
        "众人"
      ],
      "text": "丞相高见不差。告辞。",
      "text_length": 10
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02003021_e00008",
      "play_id": "02003021",
      "scene_id": "02003021_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 8,
      "seq_in_scene": 8,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "曹操"
      ],
      "text": "恕不远送。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02003021_e00009",
      "play_id": "02003021",
      "scene_id": "02003021_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 9,
      "seq_in_scene": 9,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "同白",
      "speakers": [
        "众人"
      ],
      "text": "不敢当了。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02003021_e00010",
