      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "同白",
      "speakers": [
        "众人"
      ],
      "text": "请了。",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02003021_e00025",
      "play_id": "02003021",
      "scene_id": "02003021_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 25,
      "seq_in_scene": 11,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "荀彧"
      ],
      "text": "我等领了丞相之命，备酒与祢衡饯行。来，打道。",
      "text_length": 22
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02003021_e00026",
      "play_id": "02003021",
      "scene_id": "02003021_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 26,
      "seq_in_scene": 12,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "同白",
      "speakers": [
        "众人"
      ],
      "text": "请。",
      "text_length": 2
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02003021_e00027",
      "play_id": "02003021",
      "scene_id": "02003021_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 27,
      "seq_in_scene": 13,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "荀彧"
      ],
      "text": "列位大人，祢衡到此，你我都不用起身，看他如何便是。",
      "text_length": 25
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02003021_e00028",
      "play_id": "02003021",
      "scene_id": "02003021_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 28,
      "seq_in_scene": 14,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "同白",
      "speakers": [
        "众人"
      ],
      "text": "远远望见祢衡来也。",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02003021_e00029",
      "play_id": "02003021",
      "scene_id": "02003021_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 29,
      "seq_in_scene": 15,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "祢衡上。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02003021_e00030",
      "play_id": "02003021",
      "scene_id": "02003021_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 30,
      "seq_in_scene": 16,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "唱",
      "speakers": [
        "祢衡"
      ],
      "text": "祢衡马上自嗟叹，古今事来颠倒颠。高祖去赴鸿门宴，西汉相争四百年。曹操中原虚扶汉，一心想谋汉江山。孔融无谋将我荐，曹瞒肉眼不识贤。催马来在长亭看，里面坐定文武官。荀彧、荀攸智谋浅，郭嘉程昱亦等闲。必是与我把行饯，停鞭忙下马雕鞍。",
      "text_length": 113
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02003021_e00031",
      "play_id": "02003021",
      "scene_id": "02003021_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 31,
      "seq_in_scene": 17,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "祢衡"
      ],
      "text": "来此长亭之上，里面坐的尽都是曹操谋士，须要以礼相待。列位先生请了。",
      "text_length": 33
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02003021_e00032",
      "play_id": "02003021",
      "scene_id": "02003021_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 32,
      "seq_in_scene": 18,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "同白",
      "speakers": [
        "众人"
      ],
      "text": "我等不得远迎。",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02003021_e00033",
      "play_id": "02003021",
      "scene_id": "02003021_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 33,
      "seq_in_scene": 19,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "祢衡"
      ],
      "text": "少待。俺日前进府，与曹操深施一礼，他昂然不动。今日长亭，连他众谋士也是这等大模大样。他们轻慢于我，但取笑一番。他有来言，我有去语。吓。",
      "text_length": 67
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02003021_e00034",
      "play_id": "02003021",
      "scene_id": "02003021_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 34,
      "seq_in_scene": 20,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "唱",
      "speakers": [
        "祢衡"
      ],
      "text": "四海相逢初见面，人生须得礼为先。长亭假装把泪展，问我一声回一言。",
      "text_length": 32
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02003021_e00035",
      "play_id": "02003021",
      "scene_id": "02003021_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 35,
      "seq_in_scene": 21,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "同白",
      "speakers": [
        "众人"
      ],
      "text": "祢衡见了我等，为何啼哭？",
      "text_length": 12
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02003021_e00036",
      "play_id": "02003021",
      "scene_id": "02003021_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 36,
      "seq_in_scene": 22,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "唱",
      "speakers": [
        "祢衡"
      ],
      "text": "非是祢衡泪不干，我今有言听心间：指望来在古阳关，谁知来在灵棺前。",
      "text_length": 32
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02003021_e00037",
      "play_id": "02003021",
      "scene_id": "02003021_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 37,
      "seq_in_scene": 23,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "同白",
      "speakers": [
        "众人"
      ],
      "text": "胆大狂徒。我等死尸，你乃无头狂鬼。尚不知耻！",
      "text_length": 22
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02003021_e00038",
      "play_id": "02003021",
      "scene_id": "02003021_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 38,
      "seq_in_scene": 24,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "祢衡"
      ],
      "text": "俺本大丈夫，汉朝之臣，不做曹操之党。某怎得无头？",
      "text_length": 24
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02003021_e00039",
      "play_id": "02003021",
      "scene_id": "02003021_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 39,
      "seq_in_scene": 25,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "同白",
      "speakers": [
        "众人"
      ],
      "text": "俺丞相福大量大，不与你计较。荆州刘表，性如烈火。你若出言不逊，将你一刀分为两段，岂不是无头狂鬼？",
      "text_length": 48
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02003021_e00040",
      "play_id": "02003021",
      "scene_id": "02003021_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 40,
      "seq_in_scene": 26,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "祢衡"
      ],
      "text": "俺祢衡宁做他乡之鬼，不做贼佞之臣！岂你等趋炎附势，只图眼前富贵，那知臭名万载。无耻之辈，不足与吾谈论。",
      "text_length": 51
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02003021_e00041",
      "play_id": "02003021",
      "scene_id": "02003021_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 41,
      "seq_in_scene": 27,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "同白",
      "speakers": [
        "众人"
      ],
      "text": "你乃无耻之辈。胸中有什么策议，出此狂言？",
      "text_length": 20
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02003021_e00042",
      "play_id": "02003021",
      "scene_id": "02003021_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 42,
      "seq_in_scene": 28,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "祢衡"
      ],
      "text": "要问我胸中策论，展开你们驴耳，听俺道来。",
      "text_length": 20
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02003021_e00043",
      "play_id": "02003021",
      "scene_id": "02003021_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 43,
      "seq_in_scene": 29,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "唱",
      "speakers": [
        "祢衡"
      ],
      "text": "你道俺胸中无策论，战国、春秋日夜精。上能治国如尧舜，下能安邦保黎民。安排摆兵和布阵，可比韩信赛陈平。有日大展经纶手，要把贼子一笔倾。",
      "text_length": 66
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02003021_e00044",
      "play_id": "02003021",
      "scene_id": "02003021_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 44,
      "seq_in_scene": 30,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "唱",
      "speakers": [
        "荀彧"
      ],
      "text": "胆大狂徒乱舌根，自负才高夸己能。三军满斟葡萄酒，丞相之命敢不遵？你今领吾一杯酒，好去他乡做鬼魂。",
      "text_length": 48
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02003021_e00045",
      "play_id": "02003021",
      "scene_id": "02003021_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 45,
      "seq_in_scene": 31,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "唱",
      "speakers": [
        "祢衡"
      ],
      "text": "用手接过酒一樽，将杯不饮奠埃尘。非是祢衡酒不饮，先奠荀彧死尸灵。",
      "text_length": 32
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02003021_e00046",
      "play_id": "02003021",
      "scene_id": "02003021_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 46,
      "seq_in_scene": 32,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "唱",
      "speakers": [
        "荀攸"
      ],
      "text": "手捧葡萄酒一樽，我与祢衡来饯行。你今饮吾一杯酒，但愿此去早归阴！",
      "text_length": 32
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02003021_e00047",
      "play_id": "02003021",
      "scene_id": "02003021_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 47,
      "seq_in_scene": 33,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "唱",
      "speakers": [
        "祢衡"
      ],
      "text": "荀攸须为汉朝臣，今做曹操帐下宾。将酒奠在尘埃地，管叫你千年万载落骂名。",
      "text_length": 35
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02003021_e00048",
      "play_id": "02003021",
      "scene_id": "02003021_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 48,
      "seq_in_scene": 34,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "唱",
      "speakers": [
        "程昱"
      ],
      "text": "阳关饯行酒一樽，一腔恶气往上喷。若不奉了丞相命，岂肯敬酒与狂生？",
      "text_length": 32
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02003021_e00049",
      "play_id": "02003021",
      "scene_id": "02003021_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 49,
      "seq_in_scene": 35,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "唱",
      "speakers": [
        "祢衡"
      ],
      "text": "臣报君恩子奉亲，你本不忠不孝人。将酒奠在尘埃地，天雷霹死儿当身。",
      "text_length": 32
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02003021_e00050",
      "play_id": "02003021",
      "scene_id": "02003021_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 50,
      "seq_in_scene": 36,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "唱",
      "speakers": [
        "郭嘉"
      ],
      "text": "郭嘉奉酒泪淋淋，手捧葡萄吊亡魂。你今饮干吾的酒，但愿早死早脱身。",
      "text_length": 32
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02003021_e00051",
      "play_id": "02003021",
      "scene_id": "02003021_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 51,
      "seq_in_scene": 37,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "唱",
      "speakers": [
        "祢衡"
      ],
      "text": "郭嘉不必两泪淋，短命年少小姣生。吾去荆州有不幸，儿是披麻戴孝人。将酒奠在尘埃地，有事关心少留停。手扳雕鞍足踏蹬，还有一事少叮咛。回头我对群臣论，贼子狗党仔细听：我本天上东斗星，亦非凡间等闲人。只因有事犯了罪，将俺谪贬下凡尘；赐我一口青龙剑，杀却朝中狗谗臣。你等回复曹奸佞：宽心稳坐听信音。若得刘表来归顺，祢衡当朝做公卿；我今去后无音信，却是孝子与贤孙。在此不与你谈论，跨马扬鞭走一程。",
      "text_length": 192
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02003021_e00052",
      "play_id": "02003021",
      "scene_id": "02003021_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 52,
      "seq_in_scene": 38,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "祢衡笑，下。",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02003021_e00053",
      "play_id": "02003021",
      "scene_id": "02003021_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 53,
      "seq_in_scene": 39,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "同唱",
      "speakers": [
        "众人"
      ],
      "text": "长亭去了祢正平，去时有路回无门。",
      "text_length": 16
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02003021_e00054",
      "play_id": "02003021",
      "scene_id": "02003021_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 54,
      "seq_in_scene": 40,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "荀彧"
      ],
      "text": "列位先生，祢衡言语狂妄，荆州吉凶难料。你我回复丞相。",
      "text_length": 26
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02003021_e00055",
      "play_id": "02003021",
      "scene_id": "02003021_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 55,
      "seq_in_scene": 41,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "同白",
      "speakers": [
        "众人"
      ],
      "text": "左右，带马回府交令去者。",
      "text_length": 12
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02003021_e00056",
      "play_id": "02003021",
      "scene_id": "02003021_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 56,
      "seq_in_scene": 42,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "众人同下。——————————⑴本场接《打鼓骂曹》最后一场。",
      "text_length": 30
    }
  ],
  "roles_inferred": true
}